WORK SUMMARY :
In this session we gained the knowledge on fundamentals of user authentication systems and explored how secure login and signup mechanisms are implemented in 
modern applications. The objective of this session was to build a strong foundation in authentication concepts and understand how user data is protected and verified 
efficiently in real-world scenarios  and  learned how authentication is used in applications such as e-commerce platforms, social media, and banking systems to ensure 
that only authorized users can access sensitive data and perform actions securely.
